title: #92Noon! Montage/Birk&Siny/Bercich/Lavelle
description: 0-3 Vikings fodder to begin, Twins are in the playoffs, Matt Birk and Dave Sinykin both join to end the first hour, Pete Bercich in studio for most of the 10a stretch, then more Vikings and Lavelle hangs out for the final hour to pump up his Bears and playoff-bound Twins!
